latestPosts.caption:
danced with the sweetestttt @shraddhakapoor today!!!! Aaaahhhhhgghhh SO SO MUCH FUN! 

Thank you @metaindia @ankit_rihal for such a fun evening 💙

Got myself an MBA from the #1 B-School in India. Made it through one of the most challenging years of my life. Met the smartest and most talented bunch of people, many of whom I have the privilege of calling my closets friends. 

Cried a lot, laughed a lot, learned a lot. (danced a lot too)

However this post is specifically for you. 

Thank you for sticking by and coming with me on this journey. It was truly a roller coaster and while I tried to create as much content as possible, there were days when I really struggled with time. I know I haven’t been the most consistent creator this year simply because of the sheer workload and the number of events assignments, exams and what not. But inspite of that, you stayed. And showed so so much love! It really made the hard times easier and the fun times more enjoyable because I was excited to share them with you. 

Cannot be more grateful for this community of 350K. 

Thank you to each and every one of you! 

#graduated
